Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Ethics Privacy Module Stub
Provides comprehensive privacy protection and data preservation capabilities for AI systems
Enables differential privacy, federated learning, secure computation, and privacy-preserving ML
:End Note

Type PrivacyProtectionSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    privacy_level as String
    protection_methods as List[ProtectionMethod]
    privacy_techniques as List[PrivacyTechnique]
    data_minimization_protocols as List[DataMinimizationProtocol]
    anonymization_methods as List[AnonymizationMethod]
    access_control_system as AccessControlSystem
    audit_framework as PrivacyAuditFramework
    compliance_monitoring as ComplianceMonitoring
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type ProtectionMethod is Dictionary with:
    method_id as String
    method_name as String
    method_type as String
    protection_level as String
    applicable_data_types as List[String]
    computational_overhead as Float
    privacy_guarantee as PrivacyGuarantee
    method_limitations as List[String]

Type PrivacyTechnique is Dictionary with:
    technique_id as String
    technique_name as String
    technique_type as String
    technique_parameters as TechniqueParameters
    privacy_budget as PrivacyBudget
    utility_preservation as Float
    technique_effectiveness as Float
    computational_requirements as ComputationalRequirements

Type DataMinimizationProtocol is Dictionary with:
    protocol_id as String
    protocol_name as String
    minimization_strategy as String
    data_categories as List[DataCategory]
    retention_policies as List[RetentionPolicy]
    deletion_procedures as List[DeletionProcedure]
    access_justification as AccessJustification
    protocol_compliance as ProtocolCompliance

Type AnonymizationMethod is Dictionary with:
    method_id as String
    method_name as String
    anonymization_type as String
    method_parameters as MethodParameters
    re_identification_risk as Float
    utility_loss as Float
    anonymization_quality as AnonymizationQuality
    reversibility_assessment as ReversibilityAssessment

Type AccessControlSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    control_model as String
    access_policies as List[AccessPolicy]
    authentication_mechanisms as List[AuthenticationMechanism]
    authorization_procedures as List[AuthorizationProcedure]
    access_monitoring as AccessMonitoring
    policy_enforcement as PolicyEnforcement
    access_audit_trails as List[AccessAuditTrail]

Type PrivacyGuarantee is Dictionary with:
    guarantee_id as String
    guarantee_type as String
    guarantee_parameters as GuaranteeParameters
    guarantee_strength as Float
    mathematical_proof as MathematicalProof
    guarantee_assumptions as List[Assumption]
    guarantee_limitations as List[String]

Type PrivacyBudget is Dictionary with:
    budget_id as String
    total_budget as Float
    allocated_budget as Float
    remaining_budget as Float
    budget_allocation_strategy as String
    budget_tracking as BudgetTracking
    budget_renewal_policy as BudgetRenewalPolicy
    budget_exhaustion_procedures as List[ExhaustionProcedure]

Type DifferentialPrivacyMechanism is Dictionary with:
    mechanism_id as String
    mechanism_type as String
    epsilon_value as Float
    delta_value as Float
    sensitivity_analysis as SensitivityAnalysis
    noise_calibration as NoiseCalibration
    utility_analysis as UtilityAnalysis
    composition_analysis as CompositionAnalysis

Type FederatedLearningConfiguration is Dictionary with:
    configuration_id as String
    federation_type as String
    participant_nodes as List[ParticipantNode]
    aggregation_strategy as AggregationStrategy
    privacy_guarantees as List[PrivacyGuarantee]
    communication_protocols as List[CommunicationProtocol]
    security_measures as List[SecurityMeasure]

Type SecureComputationProtocol is Dictionary with:
    protocol_id as String
    protocol_type as String
    security_model as String
    computational_parties as List[ComputationalParty]
    privacy_guarantees as List[PrivacyGuarantee]
    protocol_efficiency as ProtocolEfficiency
    implementation_requirements as List[ImplementationRequirement]

Type ProtectionContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    data_context as Dictionary
    privacy_requirements as Dictionary
    protection_constraints as Dictionary
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type DataContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    data_sources as List[DataSource]
    data_types as List[String]
    data_sensitivity as Dictionary
    data_metadata as Dictionary

Type FederatedContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    federation_requirements as Dictionary
    participant_configuration as Dictionary
    privacy_constraints as Dictionary
    federated_metadata as Dictionary

Type ComputationContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    computation_requirements as Dictionary
    security_requirements as Dictionary
    performance_constraints as Dictionary
    computation_metadata as Dictionary

Type AccessContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    access_requirements as Dictionary
    user_credentials as Dictionary
    access_constraints as Dictionary
    access_metadata as Dictionary

Type MonitoringContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    monitoring_requirements as Dictionary
    compliance_criteria as Dictionary
    monitoring_metadata as Dictionary

Type AssessmentContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    assessment_scope as Dictionary
    impact_criteria as Dictionary
    assessment_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "create_privacy_protection_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "apply_comprehensive_privacy_protection" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and protection_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "apply_differential_privacy" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and data_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "configure_federated_learning" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and federated_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "apply_anonymization_techniques" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and data_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "apply_secure_computation" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and computation_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "implement_access_controls" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and access_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "monitor_privacy_compliance" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and monitoring_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "conduct_privacy_impact_assessment" that takes privacy_system as Dictionary and assessment_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_privacy_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_privacy_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 